data.name: GalaxyMC Server
data.description:
🌌 Unique Features of GalaxyMC

✨ Smooth & Lag-Free Gameplay
Optimized performance for a smooth Minecraft experience, even with many players online.

🛡️ Active Staff & Fair Play
Friendly and active staff keep the server safe, hacker-free, and enjoyable for everyone.

🎮 Fun Commands & Systems
Easy-to-use game and Discord commands to enhance gameplay and interaction.

🏰 Creative & Survival Friendly
Build freely, explore worlds, and enjoy survival with balanced mechanics.

🎉 Regular Events & Giveaways
Exciting events, competitions, and rewards coming regularly to keep things fun.

🐞 Quick Bug Fix System
Dedicated bug-report channel ensures fast fixes and continuous improvement.

💬 Chill & Fun Community
Memes, screenshots, trash-talk, and chats — a place to relax and enjoy.

🤖 Smart Discord Integration
Invite tracking, welcome system, reports, and bot features fully integrated.

🌍 Beginner Friendly
New players are always welcome with guidance and support.

🚀 Always Improving
GalaxyMC is constantly updating with new ideas, features, and content.
